    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334660/extras/8730af7aadd5fb5d8ceab5ab9cc8ce4a.avif?t=1762595932\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334660/extras_big/8730af7aadd5fb5d8ceab5ab9cc8ce4a.avif?t=1762595932 width=800 height=281 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334660/extras/9360eb937f87a5ab53418f849d8be99c.avif?t=1762595932\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334660/extras_big/9360eb937f87a5ab53418f849d8be99c.avif?t=1762595932 width=800 height=188 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334660/extras/475973a2d509c2cdb962e3af05724ea5.poster.avif?t=1762595932\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334660/extras/475973a2d509c2cdb962e3af05724ea5.webm?t=1762595932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334660/extras/475973a2d509c2cdb962e3af05724ea5.mp4?t=1762595932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334660/extras/d79e9adc0f524aa3bd7c39ef7c1854db.avif?t=1762595932\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334660/extras_big/d79e9adc0f524aa3bd7c39ef7c1854db.avif?t=1762595932 width=800 height=354 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>如果电脑里有生物会怎样？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >微灵是一种生活在数字环境中的数据型生物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它们能够自主思考，并且像人类一样拥有幸福和抑郁等情感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在现代社会，微灵被认为是重要的生物，并被归类为生命体。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >国家对微灵实行严格管理和保护，小微灵在【微灵存储库】中安全成长。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成年微灵会被分配各种角色并从事工作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因此，个人饲微灵是非法的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>诶？……你想要微灵吗？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>啊，那你来对地方了。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你也可以在这里养小微灵。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>5只拥有独特个性的微灵</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>可爱的像素画风独特微灵在等着你！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334660/extras/fe0fc21fde8b227bc0aecf38a251fe40.avif?t=1762595932\" width=800 height=798 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >残酷的童话故事</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你购买非法程序【微灵】，你将卷入一个震惊且残酷的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >亲自体验隐藏在可爱画面背后的剧情反转吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334660/extras/15838b45f83fae0055b0406ea79fdd87.avif?t=1762595932\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334660/extras_big/15838b45f83fae0055b0406ea79fdd87.avif?t=1762595932 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334660/extras/364844d72ea6e4c387f073f4a8a5abe4.poster.avif?t=1762595932\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334660/extras/364844d72ea6e4c387f073f4a8a5abe4.webm?t=1762595932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334660/extras/364844d72ea6e4c387f073f4a8a5abe4.mp4?t=1762595932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2D与3D的完美融合</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在3D游戏中，与微灵一起合作解决故事中的问题！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >草地上熟悉的东西。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334660/extras/1d57365bdfd63e1c8a39af43ef5ff532.avif?t=1762595932\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334660/extras_big/1d57365bdfd63e1c8a39af43ef5ff532.avif?t=1762595932 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >电脑里出现了一个错误……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其实，这并不是简单的系统故障。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334660/extras/cfafa2665b53b40ff073847404e03e85.avif?t=1762595932\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334660/extras_big/cfafa2665b53b40ff073847404e03e85.avif?t=1762595932 width=800 height=446 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334660/extras/200e07ec7dc5c8066bbf0e23f2b87e4f.poster.avif?t=1762595932\" width=800 height=648 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334660/extras/200e07ec7dc5c8066bbf0e23f2b87e4f.webm?t=1762595932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334660/extras/200e07ec7dc5c8066bbf0e23f2b87e4f.mp4?t=1762595